{"tid":1773462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淘大和你唱重申五大訴求 多間商舖提早落閘","createTime":"2019-12-07T13:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T13:24:23.000Z","uid":125168,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b73081cec84e2ed41fc8108fec87d50a90f63847","tid":1773462,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"有市民在淘大商場參與「和你唱」重申五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n有市民發起晚上於九龍灣淘大商場「和你唱」活動，重申五大訴求，部分人戴口罩，商場多間商舖提早落閘。 晚上7時半後，陸續有市民在淘大商場聚集，大批市民不斷高呼「五大訴求，缺一不可」、「解散警隊，刻不容緩」，並高叫「12.8，維園見」等口號。有市民亮起手機燈，唱出《願榮光歸香港》、《Do You Hear the People Sing》等反修例歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-07 20:58:38"},{"pid":"cf02e0e14b937ca65525ab5a9f1a511b0ada4370","tid":1773462,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"rthk tg news<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b67e5c3762c71d846b5e33b08414d39b4e000e","tid":1773462,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac67f72c67f431839ed77185800c52e0be1f616d","tid":1773462,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"分分鐘淘大仲多人過今日撐警集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71b23325858c0df4404044b5069f5147b8d9d61","tid":1773462,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"點解次次都淘大避開德福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}